data.description:
Spacious 4 bedroom, 2 bath rambler located just a few blocks from White Bear Lake. This beautiful 
home features:  Enormous kitchen with many cabinets and large eating area along with breakfast,  
dining room, New carpet in 2023, Hardwood floors, 3 Bedrooms on the main floor, finished lower-level with 4th Bedroom, Large family room with ceramic tile, 3/4 bath and much storage space. Other amenities include: New Central Air in 2021, New Furnace in 2020, Fenced yard, Deck, Storage Shed, 2 Car attached garage, Concrete driveway, and more. Priced to sell fast.
